characterDescription.skinTone: fair skin with neutral undertones, a hint of pink on the cheeks and forehead, skin appears smooth and delicate
characterDescription.eyeColor: bright sky blue eyes with a slightly darker limbal ring, giving them a defined edge
characterDescription.eyeShape: almond-shaped eyes, slightly tilted upwards at the outer corners, with full upper eyelids and somewhat noticeable under-eye circles
characterDescription.hairColor: medium-dark chestnut brown with subtle natural lighter highlights throughout
characterDescription.hairTexture: fine, slightly wavy hair with some loose curls, especially around the face
characterDescription.hairStyle: hair styled in two high buns on top of the head, secured with pink hair clips adorned with fluffy white pom-poms, loose strands framing the face
characterDescription.faceShape: oval face with rounded cheeks, soft jawline, and a slightly pointed chin
characterDescription.nose: small, slightly upturned nose with a rounded tip, bridge is straight and narrow
characterDescription.lips: medium-sized lips with a defined Cupid's bow, natural pink color, slightly fuller bottom lip
characterDescription.smile: slight, subtle smile with lips pressed together, not showing teeth, a hint of seriousness in her expression
characterDescription.eyebrows: medium-thick, naturally arched eyebrows, slightly darker than her hair color, well-defined
characterDescription.ears: visible medium-sized ears, with attached earlobes and subtle folds and curves
characterDescription.cheeks: full, rounded cheeks with a slight flush of pink
characterDescription.chin: slightly pointed chin, proportionate to the rest of her face
characterDescription.facialProportions: eyes are large and prominent relative to the face, nose and mouth are proportionally smaller, giving her a delicate appearance
characterDescription.distinctiveFeatures: the blue ink stain on the back of her left hand near her knuckles, subtle freckles across the bridge of her nose, slightly downturned corners of the mouth give her a unique expression
characterDescription.overallImpression: sweet and slightly serious appearance, with a touch of mischief in her eyes, her features are delicate and well-proportioned
characterDescription.fullDescription: This is a 5-6 year old girl with fair skin and neutral undertones, and bright sky blue, almond-shaped eyes that are slightly upturned. Her hair is medium-dark chestnut brown, fine and slightly wavy with loose curls, styled in two high buns secured with pink pom-pom clips. She has a small upturned nose and medium pink lips with a subtle smile, giving her a sweet and serious expression, and she has a blue ink stain on her left hand. Her eyebrows are medium-thick, naturally arched, slightly darker than her hair color and she has subtle freckles across the bridge of her nose.
